IMPOSED AND STAYED SENTENCE OF:   

4 MONTHS JAIL, (CREDIT - 3 days);

TERM OF PROBATION:  1 Year, (The Court would grant early termination of probation after 9 months if the the agent recommends and finds it is appropriate);

CONDITIONS OF PROBATION:  
*No contact with:  Craig K. or his residence.
*DNA sample to be provided if not yet previously done.
*Any other condition the agent deems appropriate.

COURT COSTS:  $243.00 (apply cash bail and balance to be paid as a condition of probation);

DNA SURCHARGE:  $200.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

CONDITION TIME:30 DAYS, STAYED; to be used at agent's discretion.  Agent to determine with or without non working hours.
